Compute the cosine of a number.



```kcl
cos(@num: number(Angle)): number(_)
```


### Arguments

| Name | Type | Description | Required |
|----------|------|-------------|----------|
| `num` | `number(Angle)` |  | Yes |

### Returns

`number(_)`


### Examples

```kcl
exampleSketch = startSketchOn(XZ)
  |> startProfile(at = [0, 0])
  |> angledLine(
    angle = 30,
    length = 3 / cos(30deg),
  )
  |> yLine(endAbsolute = 0)
  |> close()

example = extrude(exampleSketch, length = 5)
```
